subproject.description: The Purpose and Objectives of the Project are “Enhanced engagement in the multilevel aid coordination structure, enhanced analysis and strengthening access” through “enhanced research and monitoring and evaluation services to the PA, donors and UN” and “Enhancement of UNSCO’s relationships with its Israeli interlocutors and improve support to the Humanitarian Coordinator on access issues”.
subproject.title: MAXIMIZING IMPACT - UNSCO
